Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,袭击欧洲大陆中央的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.41,0:00:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨大 空间震
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说伤者有一亿五千万人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造成了前所未有的灾难  未曾有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.31,0:00:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
